"""Profile-only hybrid actor plus central observation timing scaffold.

This module intentionally does not call LightZero training. It keeps CurvyTron
stepping behind small in-process actor objects, merges compact row metadata in a
parent-shaped manager, builds zero ``[B, P, 4, 64, 64]`` stacks, and materializes
scalar LightZero-shaped rows only at the outer edge for throughput profiling.
"""

